123
00:08:59.956 --> 00:09:02.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¡Tú también nos has mentido!

124
00:09:02.959 --> 00:09:05.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
